<keyLead lastPageId="14" lastPageNumber="15" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">- Sporophytes ventral at the thallus apex; involucres bivalved; seta remaining short; elaters few per capsule; capsule dehiscence by a lid and irregular valves ....................................................................................................................................................................7</keyLead>
