<keyLead pageId="14" pageNumber="15">
- Thallus very thin, 2-layered, translucent; antheridia scattered in clusters along the edge of the thallus; sporophyte in an apical notch on the ventral thallus surface; foot and seta of sporophyte represented by a single filament ..................................... 
<taxonomicName box="[1300,1451,389,411]" class="Marchantiopsida" family="Cyathodiaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Marchantiales" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" phylum="Marchantiophyta" rank="family">
